        </div>
    </a>
</div>

<div class="welcome-footer">
    <a class="welcome-footer__link">
        <h3>Webinars</h3>
        <p>Live online classes. Pick the brains of our experts.</p>
    </a>
    <a class="welcome-footer__link">
        <h3>Help Center</h3>
        <p>Our knowledge base and FAQs.</p>
    </a>
    <a class="welcome-footer__link">
        <h3>Support</h3>
        <p>Friendly experts, always ready to help.</p>
    </a>
</div>

